***UP TO 6k TOWARDS RATE BUYDOWN AND/OR CLOSING COSTS (INCL APPRAISAL CREDIT) IF USING PREFERRED LENDER W/ FULL PRICE OFFER***
DON'T MISS OUT ON THIS COMPLETELY RENOVATED, well-maintained home with lots of recent upgrades. NEW ROOF, NEW FLOORING, UPDATED KITCHEN and BATH, NEW hurricane windows and sliding glass door, and complete smart home security system (Vivint). 

Enjoy a dedicated playground and dog park within the small and quaint community. Close proximity to the airport and both Towncenters, which offer a plethora of shopping and dining options.
